log(2) ~ 0.693 used for conversion of half-life injection time to injection rate.
Complex reaction kinetics by CYP2D6. Reaction kinetics contains competitive inhibition by quinidine, is affected by CYP2D6 activity score.

This reaction is required for the poor metabolizer phenotype, which have no CYP2D6 activity. A basal low conversion exists independent of CYP2D6 phenotype. 2021-09-08|janekg: CYP mediated conversion of DXM to DXO normally accounting for a low percentage of conversion.

CYP3A4 mediated conversion of DXM is responsible for the first-pass metabolism of DXM, dextromethorphan (DXM) -[CYP3A4]-> 3-methoxymorphinan (MEM/MM3).First pass can occur in intestine and liver and both enzymes are modeled via the same parameters (Km, Vmax). CYP3A4 inhibition/activation can be implemented by changing the CYP3A4_activity, e.g., grapefruit juice selectively inhibits only the intestinal CYP3A4.
